when you're styling your hair?

283
00:33:29,241 --> 00:33:30,521
Shit.

284
00:33:32,369 --> 00:33:36,747
Sometimes I wonder
if players today have it in here.

285
00:33:36,874 --> 00:33:39,958
You know what Gordie Howe's
bonus was when he signed?

286
00:33:40,085 --> 00:33:42,541
