287
00:33:42,672 --> 00:33:44,499
Lousy agent.

288
00:33:44,632 --> 00:33:50,836
Now everybody wants a 20-year no-cut
contract and a second home in Bora Bora.

289
00:33:50,972 --> 00:33:52,003
Where's that?

290
00:33:52,140 --> 00:33:54,512
The way you looked at practice this week,

291
00:33:54,643 --> 00:33:59,519
you'll be lucky if you're drafted
by the Tallahassee Warthogs.

292
00:33:59,649 --> 00:34:03,598
