302
00:35:15,230 --> 00:35:16,772
(whistle)

303
00:35:22,737 --> 00:35:25,941
- Stay on side, Youngblood.
- Pass the puck.

304
00:35:27,243 --> 00:35:31,537
- Don't tell me when to pass the puck.
- You want me to slow down for you?

305
00:35:31,664 --> 00:35:34,119
