some other time.

306
00:35:34,250 --> 00:35:37,999
I got another game to work next week,
if you don't mind.

307
00:35:38,129 --> 00:35:41,214
(player) Come on, ref! Drop it!

308
00:35:46,137 --> 00:35:48,177
Here, back.

309
00:35:52,061 --> 00:35:54,979
- Come on, I'm open.
- Don't play with it. Move it.

310
00:35:55,106 --> 00:35:57,229
Now!

311
00:35:59,694 --> 00:36:02,897
- Back! I'm open!
- Take it in!

312
00:36:03,031 --> 00:36:05,902
