skating together for years.

313
00:36:06,034 --> 00:36:10,743
Youngblood moves into the Toronto zone.
He's really showing some speed.

314
00:36:12,666 --> 00:36:14,208
(opponent) I got him!

315
00:36:14,335 --> 00:36:16,743
He moves to his left.
He skates around them.

316
00:36:19,048 --> 00:36:20,922
He's in alone on the goalie.

317
00:36:22,927 --> 00:36:25,881
- He scores!
- Way to go, Youngblood!

318
00:36:26,014 --> 00:36:28,090
(laughter)

319
00:36:29,184 --> 00:36:30,643
Shh!

320
00:36:30,769 --> 00:36:34,602
- Who's winning?
- Mustangs.

321
00:36:59,133 --> 00:37:03,000
(PA) Scoring for Hamilton,
number ten, Dean Youngblood.

322
00:37:03,137 --> 00:37:06,672
Assist from number nine, Derek Sutton.

323
00:37:06,808 --> 00:37:08,848
Nice move, rookie.

324
00:37:12,105 --> 00:37:15,225
Rossini, take Youngblood's next shift.

325
00:38:21,805 --> 00:38:22,968
Jessie.

326
00:38:39,366 --> 00:38:41,193
Oh! Agh!

327
00:38:58,970 --> 00:39:00,298
Dean?

328
00:39:00,430 --> 00:39:03,135
Is there any blood?

329
00:39:03,266 --> 00:39:05,972
You son of a bitch.

330
00:39:06,103 --> 00:39:11,144
Hockey players love the sight of blood.
Especially their own.

331
00:39:18,366 --> 00:39:20,774
I scored a goal.

332
00:39:21,577 --> 00:39:24,947
Really? I don't follow hockey.

333
00:39:25,081 --> 00:39:27,121
Or hockey players.

334
00:39:31,505 --> 00:39:35,087
You know, your dad benched me.

335
00:39:35,217 --> 00:39:38,052
Derek says it's because I'm seeing you.

336
00:39:42,225 --> 00:39:44,265
Maybe he's right.

337
00:39:46,229 --> 00:39:50,143
If I'm getting benched for something
I didn't do, I might as well do it.

338
00:39:50,275 --> 00:39:53,193
- Do what?
- Take you out.

339
00:39:55,990 --> 00:40:01,660
- Why do you think I'll go out with you?
- Cos your old man doesn't want you to.

340
00:40:03,998 --> 00:40:06,536
Sounds like a pretty good reason.

341
00:40:17,346 --> 00:40:19,386
(waltz music)

342
00:40:28,274 --> 00:40:32,059
It doesn't look like a Mustangs practice,
that's for sure.

343
00:40:32,195 --> 00:40:34,651
