when you're growing up.

456
00:54:19,959 --> 00:54:24,420
Then you realise
that it's more than just a game.

457
00:54:24,547 --> 00:54:28,130
You gotta play it according to their rules.

458
00:54:34,267 --> 00:54:36,805
Do you still like playing?

459
00:54:38,729 --> 00:54:40,769
Fucking love it.

460
00:54:55,873 --> 00:55:02,374
